sentences: On Friday, 27 March, the AWG-LCA Chair Michael Zammit Cutajar (Malta) presented his document on the fulfillment of the Bali Action Plan and components of the agreed outcome ( FCCC/AWGLCA/2009/4 , Parts I and II).

AWG-KP Chair Harald Dovland (Norway) presented his notes on the flexibility mechanisms ( FCCC/KP/AWG/2009/INF.2 ), LULUCF (FCCC/KP/AWG/2009/INF.1), amendments pursuant to Protocol Article 3.9 ( FCCC/KP/AWG/2009/3 ) and elements of text related to issues in paragraph 49 ( FCCC/KP/AWG/2009/4 ).
enb_long_title: Fifth session of the Ad Hoc Working Group on Long-term Cooperative Action under the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change (AWG-LCA 5) and Seventh session of the Ad Hoc Working Group on Further Commitments for Annex I Parties under the Kyoto Protocol (AWG-KP 7)
